      <title>Dirichlet&#39;s Hyperbola Method</title>
      <link href="blog/Dhm/"/>
      <url>blog/Dhm/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><div class="note success modern"><p>[Dirichlet’s hyperbola method]<br>      若 $ f=g*h $.则对正实数 $y$，</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">  \sum_{n \le x} f(n)=\sum_{d \le y} g(d) H\left(\frac{x}{d}\right)+\sum_{d \le \frac{x}{y}} h(d) G\left(\frac{x}{d}\right)-G(y) H\left(\frac{x}{y}\right)</script><p>或是</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \sum_{n \le x} f(n)=\sum_{n \leq x} \sum_{a b=n} g(a) h(b)=\sum_{a \leq \sqrt{x}} \sum_{b \leq \frac{x}{a}} g(a) h(b)+\sum_{b \leq \sqrt{x}} \sum_{a \leq \frac{x}{b}} g(a) h(b)-\sum_{a \leq \sqrt{x}} \sum_{b \leq \sqrt{x}} g(a) h(b)</script></div><p>Dirichlet双曲方法的名字就来源于求和$ \sum_{ab \le x} 1 $的几何意义,即双曲线 $ab = x$ 与$x$轴之间的整点的个数.</p><p>其实，若$f=g*h$,则有</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \sum_{n\le x}f(n)=\sum_{n\le x}\sum_{ab=n}g(a)h(b)=\sum_{ab\le x}g(a)h(b)</script><p>将$a$固定只对$b$求和,就有</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \sum_{n\le x}f(n)=\sum_{a\le x}g(a)\sum_{b\le x/a}h(b)</script><p>利用这个公式可以证明</p><div class="note info modern"><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sum_{n\le x}\varphi(n)=\frac{3}{\pi^2}x^2+O(x\ln x)</script></div><div class="hide-toggle" ><div class="hide-button toggle-title" style=""><i class="fas fa-caret-right fa-fw"></i><span>证明</span></div>    <div class="hide-content"><p>首先$\varphi(n)=\mu*id$,由此</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}    \sum_{n\le x}\varphi(n)&=\sum_{a\le x}\mu(a)\sum_{b\le x/a}b\\    &=\sum_{a\le x}\mu(a)\left(\frac{x^2}{2a^2}+O(x/a)\right)\\    &=\frac{x^2}{2}\sum_{a\le x}\frac{\mu(a)}{a^2}+O\left(x\sum_{a\le x}\frac{\left|\mu(a)\right|}{a}\right)\\    &=\frac{3}{\pi^2}x^2+O(x\ln x)\end{aligned}</script><p>(细节以后有机会再补)</p></div></div><p>继续考虑满足$AB=x$的$A,B$,以$A$为界，有</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}    \sum_{n\le x}f(n)&=\sum_{\substack{ab\le x\\a\le A}}g(a)h(b)+\sum_{\substack{ab\le x\\a>A}}g(a)h(b)\\    &=\sum_{a\le A}\sum_{b\le x/a}g(a)h(b)+\sum_{b\le B}\sum_{A<a\le x/b}g(a)h(b)\\    &=\sum_{a\le A}\sum_{b\le x/a}g(a)h(b)+\sum_{b\le B}\sum_{a\le x/b}g(a)h(b)-\sum_{a\le A}g(a)\sum_{b\le B}h(b)\end{aligned}</script><p>如若我们把$g,h$都替换成$1$,那么右边会变得更清晰—这就是容斥原理：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \sum_{n\le x}f(n)=\left|X\cup Y\right|=\left|X\right|+\left|Y\right|-\left|X\cap Y\right|</script><p>此处$f(n)=1<em> 1$,$X:={(a,b)\in\mathbb{N}^2:a\le A}$,$Y:={(a,b)\in\mathbb{N}^2:b\le B}$.因为$1</em>1=d(n)$,进而得到下面的命题：</p><div class="note info modern"><p>[Dirichlet]<br>证明</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \sum_{i\le n} d(n)=n\ln n +(2\gamma-1)n+O(n)</script></div><div class="hide-toggle" ><div class="hide-button toggle-title" style=""><i class="fas fa-caret-right fa-fw"></i><span>证明</span></div>    <div class="hide-content"><p>因为$d(x)=1*1$，故</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \begin{aligned}    \sum_{n \leq x} d(n) &=\sum_{a \leq \sqrt{x}} \sum_{b \leq \frac{x}{a}} 1+\sum_{b \leq \sqrt{x}} \sum_{a \leq \frac{x}{b}} 1-\sum_{a \leq \sqrt{x}} \sum_{b \leq \sqrt{x}} 1 \\    &=\sum_{a \leq \sqrt{x}}\left(\frac{x}{a}+O(1)\right)+\sum_{b \leq \sqrt{x}}\left(\frac{x}{b}+O(1)\right)-\left(\sum_{a \leq \sqrt{x}} 1\right)\left(\sum_{b \leq \sqrt{x}} 1\right) \\    &=2 \sum_{c \leq \sqrt{x}}\left(\frac{x}{c}+O(1)\right)-\left(\sum_{c \leq \sqrt{x}} 1\right)^{2} \\    &=2 x \sum_{c \leq \sqrt{x}} \frac{1}{c}+O\left(\sum_{c \leq \sqrt{x}} 1\right)-(\sqrt{x}+O(1))^{2} \\    &=2 x\left(\ln \sqrt{x}+\gamma+O\left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{x}}\right)\right)+O(\sqrt{x})-(x+O(\sqrt{x})+O(1)) \\    &=2 x\left(\frac{1}{2} \ln x+\gamma+O\left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{x}}\right)\right)-x+O(\sqrt{x}) \\    &=x \ln x+2 \gamma x+O\left(\frac{x}{\sqrt{x}}\right)-x+O(\sqrt{x}) \\    &=x \ln x+(2 \gamma-1) x+O(\sqrt{x})    \end{aligned}</script></div></div><div class="note info modern"><p>[习题]<br>证明</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \sum_{ k\le n}\sum_{\substack{d\mid k\\d\le\sqrt k}}d=\frac23n\sqrt n+O(n\ln n)</script></div><div class="hide-toggle" ><div class="hide-button toggle-title" style=""><i class="fas fa-caret-right fa-fw"></i><span>提示</span></div>    <div class="hide-content"><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    \sum_{ k\le n}\sum_{\substack{d\mid k\\d\le\sqrt k}}d=\sum_{(x,y)\in A}y+\sum_{(x,y)\in B}y</script><p>其中</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">    A=\{(x,y):0<y\le x\le\sqrt{n}\},\quad B=\{(x,y):\sqrt{n}< x,0< y\le n/x\}</script></div></div>]]></content>
      
      
